set_pba_mode(25.10)                                        set_pba_mode(25.10)

Name
       set_pba_mode - Enables IPBA infinite depth path-based analysis (IPBA)

Syntax
       set_pba_mode

       [-help]

       [-reset]

       Enables IPBA infinite depth path-based analysis (IPBA).

       This feature runs faster analysis (vs full depth exhaustive PBA (EPBA))
       and attains PBA design coverage with no depth limit per endpoint.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       -reset Resets specified or all the options to the default value.

